snippet.title: SpongeBob SquarePants Typing - 100% PC Longplay
snippet.description: SpongeBob SquarePants Typing is a SpongeBob SquarePants video game that was released in 2004 for the PC and Mac. The video game was published by The Learning Company. This video is a full walkthrough specifically for the PC version. I do a 100% completion longplay going through the whole game and doing every possible thing. I do all of the mini-games and complete all of the lessons in the Bikini Bottom Typing Tournament.
